race.comment: RUSTY PLOUGHMAN (1) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 10 lengths into third (19.92) at Hobart in a Other over 340m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Top prospect. LIZZY MILICI (4) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when third (19.83) in a Other at Hobart. Can turn it around this time. WINEMAKER (6) is in hot form winning his last two on end, the latest jumping from this same box to score in a Grade 5 at this track (29.95). This tougher but expected to be in the finish. BEARVILLE WHOOSH (7) is not to be discarded.
